title.narrative: Support to financial investigations units in the Caribbean

description.narrative: This activity (Support to financial investigations units in the Caribbean) is a component of Caribbean Criminal Assets Recovery Programme reported by FCDO, with a funding type of 'Other bilateral donor' and a budget of £489,428. This component benefits West Indies, regional, and works in the following sector(s): Anti-corruption organisations and institutions, Security system management and reform. , with the following implementing partners: Foreign, Commonwealth and Development Office. The start date is 01-10-2012 and the end date is 30-09-2015.
